    {
      "id": "1914750c-f3ba-8014-b47b-c314f71727ef",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper looks at data from 772 students and tries to predict student performance at the end of the semester using video learning analytics and ML. The authors use data from SIS, LMS and mobile applications, use PCA and Genetic Search for feature selection and compare 8 distinct algorithms. RF achieved 88.3% accuracy and outperformed all other algorithms. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1914750c-f3ba-8014-b47b-c314f71727ef",
